- Merge [cmd_yt_downloader](file:///d:/My%20Business/My%20Projects/On-Going/Omni%20Telegram%20Bot/bot/handlers/directDownloader.py#129-150) and [cmd_insta_downloader](file:///d:/My%20Business/My%20Projects/On-Going/Omni%20Telegram%20Bot/bot/main.py#321-343) into a single `cmd_direct_download(message, url)` function
