## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification

Since there are no automated tests in this project, verification will be manual via Telegram:

1. **Start the bot** â€” run `python bot/main.py`
2. **Test `/downloader` with a YouTube URL** â€” send `/downloader https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ` and verify the quality keyboard appears
3. **Test `/downloader` with an Instagram URL** â€” send `/downloader https://www.instagram.com/reel/...` and verify it works
4. **Test `/downloader` with no URL** â€” send `/downloader`, then send a valid YouTube URL when prompted
5. **Test invalid URL** â€” send `/downloader https://www.google.com` and verify the bot rejects it with the appropriate message
6. **Test random text** â€” send `/downloader hello world` and verify rejection
7. **Test old commands no longer exist** â€” send `/ytDownloader` and `/instaDownloader` and verify they are no longer recognized
8. **Test fallback auto-detect** â€” paste a bare YouTube URL (no command) and verify it auto-downloads
